title: Yuki Museum of Art
text: opened in <a href="Ch%C5%AB%C5%8D-ku%2C%20Osaka">Chūō-ku</a>, <a href="Osaka">Osaka</a>, Japan, in 1987. The collection, built up by of <a href="kaiseki">kaiseki</a> restaurant <a href="Kitcho">Kitchō</a> fame, includes twelve <a href="Important%20Cultural%20Properties%20of%20Japan">Important Cultural Properties</a> and three <a href="Cultural%20Properties%20of%20Japan%231933%20Law%20Regarding%20the%20Preservation%20of%20Important%20Works%20of%20Fine%20Arts">Important Art Objects</a>.
